49:1 COMMENT "# Generic type dissection: match on a generic type parameter to"
49:64 EOL "\n"
50:1 COMMENT "# select code paths at compile time. During monomorphisation, the"
50:66 EOL "\n"
51:1 COMMENT "# concrete type is known and only the matching arm survives."
51:61 EOL "\n"
52:1 COMMENT "# See doc/spec.html for a class method example."
52:48 EOL "\n"
